ature-packed Premium plan.","zp.campaign.bugupgradebottom":"Upgrade now to get the most out of your Zoho BugTracker subscription.","zp.campaign.bugupgradehead":"I'm glad that you evaluated the Premium plan of Zoho BugTracker. Now that your account is in the Free plan, you would be missing out on some amazing features!","zp.campaign.bullet1":"Do more with subtasks, reminders, and recurring {0}","zp.campaign.bullet2":"Better time tracking with Gantt charts, baseline, and critical path","zp.campaign.bullet3":"Project budgeting, expense tracking, and intuitive resource utilization charts.","zp.campaign.bullet4":"Automate your workflows with Blueprints","zp.campaign.bullet5":"Integrated issue tracking and loads of integrations with Slack, Microsoft, and Google services","zp.campaign.freebottom":"All this for 10 days, for free\u2014just for you! - Start now","zp.campaign.hi":"Hi There!","zp.campaign.notification1":"Your <span class=\'font-medium\'>Zoho Projects Enterprise Edition</span> for portal","zp.campaign.notification3":"is up and ready to roll out.","zp.campaign.subheading":"Here's what you get:","zp.campaign.text1":"As a gesture of appreciation for your continued business, I'd like to offer you 10 days free trial of our feature-packed Enterprise Plan.","zp.campaign.trialend":"is ready. Activate now.","zp.campaign.trialnotification1":"Your <span class=\'font-medium\'>Zoho Projects upgrade</span> for portal","zp.campaign.upgradebottom":"To continue using the Enterprise plan features, upgrade your portal now.","zp.campaign.upgradebullet1":"Subtasks, reminders, and recurring {0}","zp.campaign.upgradeheading":"Switch to our annual subscription to enjoy:","zp.campaign.upgradetext1":"I'm glad that you evaluated the Enterprise edition of Zoho Projects. Now that your account is in the Free plan, you would be missing the following features.","zp.cascade.depconflict":"Dependency cannot be set between subtasks when parents are dependent and vice versa.","zp.cascade.depsetaler