t":"When the due date of a predecessor {0} is moved up, shift its successor {1} by the same number of hours/days.","zp.dependency.projects":"In Dependency view, you can set dependencies between any two active {0} that have proper start & end dates. Enter duration for {0} to view them here.","zp.dependency.recursive":"Oops! These {0} are already connected.","zp.dependency.remove":"Are you sure you want to remove this dependency?","zp.dependency.removed":"removed","zp.dependency.reordertasks":"Reorder {0}","zp.dependency.searching":"Searching...","zp.dependency.searchnotfound":"Search Not Found","zp.dependency.selectatask":"(Please Select a {0})","zp.dependency.selectdependency":"Select Dependency","zp.dependency.set":"Set time lag","zp.dependency.setdependency":"Set Dependency","zp.dependency.setdependencyplanalert":"Your current plan does not support time lag between tasks.","zp.dependency.settings":"Dependency Settings","zp.dependency.sf":"SF","zp.dependency.sfdependencytype":"SF - Start to Finish","zp.dependency.sfstarttofinish":"Start to Finish","zp.dependency.sftext":"starttofinish","zp.dependency.ss":"SS","zp.dependency.ssdependencytype":"SS - Start to Start","zp.dependency.ssstarttostart":"Start to Start","zp.dependency.sstext":"starttostart","zp.dependency.successor":"Successors","zp.dependency.successorcannotbeclosed":"The Successor {2} <b>' {0} '</b> cannot be closed because the predecessor {2} '<b> {1} </b>' is still open.","zp.dependency.taskdependencysetting":"{0} Dependency","zp.dependency.timelag":"Dependency time lag","zp.dependency.type":"Dependency Type","zp.dependency.unscheduledtasks":"Unscheduled {0}","zp.dependencylink.details":"Note:This setting applies only to newly created task dependencies. Existing dependencies, including manually modified ones, will remain unchanged.","zp.dependencylink.hard":"Hard Link","zp.dependencylink.harddetails":"Hard Link - Successor task dates and completion are strictly enforced by the predecessor. Any delay or incomplete status in the predecessor automatically shifts the successor schedule.","zp.dependencylink.orgdetails":"This will be the default dependency link type set across all Projects.","zp.dependencylink.projectdetails":"This will be the default dependency link type set for this project.","zp.dependencylink.soft":"Soft Link","zp.dependencylink.softdetails":"Soft Link - Successor task retains a dependency on the predecessor but is not forced to shift. Predecessor delays or incomplete status do not impact successor dates or completion.","zp.dependencylink.type":"Link Type","zp.dependencysetting.orglevelabout":"This is the default option. The default settings will no longer apply if you change your preference in the project level {0} dependency setting.","zp.dependencysetting.orgleveltitle":"Org Level {0} Dependency","zp.dependencysetting.projectlevelabout":"Project Level {0} Dependency setting is currently based on the default Org Level setting. Modify {0} Dependency setting at a project level from this section. This will override the Org Level {0} Dependency setting for the selected project.","zp.dependencysetting.projectleveltitle":"Project Level {0} Dependency","zp.dependent.updfailed":"Update failed","zp.dependentrule.alert":"At least one value is required in the primary and dependent field to proceed","zp.dependlinktype.warmsg":"Dependent type link will prevent the user from closing a {0} unless the prerequisite {1} are closed. This cannot be replicated using a custom link type.<br>Are you sure you want to disable?","zp.dependstask.notavailable":"{0} dependency is available in our Premium and Enterprise plans.","zp.dependtemplate.help1":"It's the sequence number given to {0} based on on their Start After time period. Seq.No's are used when adding dependencies.<br><br>","zp.dependtemplate.help3":"Set the Predecessors by entering the Seq.No of the dependent {0} in the 'Predecessors' column. <br><br>For example, {0} with Seq.No 6 can have Predecessors from Seq.No 1 to 5, if the Start After period of {0} 6 comes after the end time period (Start After + Duration) of all/any {1} 1 to 5. For multiple dependencies, enter the Seq.No's in the 'Predecessors' column separated by comma, example <b>1,2,4</b><br><br>","zp.dependtemplate.help4":"{1} are sorted based on the Start After time period and when you modify the Start After value, Seq.No's may change. In addition to that, if a {0} is closed, then the subsequent {0}(s) Seq.No's also get changed.<br><br>","zp.dependtemplate.help6":"Dependency cannot be set between {0}, if the start and end time period of the {0} are the same. In this case, the above message will be displayed.<br><br>","zp.dependtemplate.preddetails":"Set the Predecessors by entering the Seq.No of the dependent {0} in the 'Predecessors' column. <br><br> For example, {0} with Seq.No 6 can have Predecessors from Seq.No 1 to 5, if the Start After time period of {0} 6 comes after the end time period (Start After + Duration) of all/any {1} 1 to 5. For multiple dependencies, enter the Seq.No's in the 'Predecessors' column separated by comma, example <b>1,2,4</b>","zp.dependtemplate.q2":"How to change the values ({0}, Duration, Start After etc)?<br>","zp.dependview.dependhelp":"Task Dependency Help","zp.dependview.dependmsg":"Only {0} with start & end date will be displayed in this view.","zp.dependview.deplist":"Dependency List","zp.dependview.finish":"Finish","zp.dependview.help1":"It's the sequence number given to {0} based on start date. Seq.No's are used when adding dependencies.<br><br>","zp.dependview.help2":"Click on a cell value to get a text box. Change the value and 'Enter' to save the values.<br><br>","zp.dependview.help3":"Set the Predecessors by entering the Seq.No of the dependent {0} in the 'Predecessors' column. <br><br>For example, {0} with Seq.No 6 can have Predecessors from Seq.No 1 to 5, if the start date of {0} 6 comes after the end date of all/any {1} 1 to 5. For multiple dependencies, enter the Seq.No's in the 'Predecessors' column separated by comma, example <b>1,2,4</b><br><br>","zp.dependview.help4":"{1} are sorted by start date and when start dates get changed, Seq.No's may change. In addition to that, if a {0} is closed, then the subsequent {0}(s) Seq.No's also get changed.<br><br>","zp.dependview.help5":"By default, only open {1} are listed. Closed {1} are listed only when there are open dependent {0}(s).<br><br>","zp.dependview.help6":"Dependency cannot be set between {0} if the start & end date of the {0} are the same. In this case, the above message will be displayed.<br><br>","zp.dependview.help7":"This message occurs when user tries to close the child {0} without completing the parent {0}.<br>","zp.dependview.helpheader":"In {0} Dependency View ...","zp.dependview.milestone":"{0} Name","zp.dependview.names":"Resource Names","zp.dependview.newhelp1":"Only {0} with valid dates will be displayed.","zp.dependview.newhelp2":"Subtasks will be displayed  if and only if all its parent {0} are displayed.","zp.dependview.preddetails":"Set predecessors by entering the seq. no of the dependent {0} in the 'Predecessors' column. <br><br> For example, {0} with seq. no 6 can have predecessors from seq. no 1 to 5, if the start date of {0} 6 comes after the end date of all/any {1} 1 to 5. For multiple dependencies, enter the seq. no's in the 'Predecessors' column separated by comma, example <b>1,2,4</b>","zp.dependview.predecessor":"Predecessors","zp.dependview.q1":"What is Seq.No?<br>","zp.dependview.q2":"How to change the values ({0}, Duration, Start Date etc)?<br>","zp.dependview.q3":"How to set Predecessors?<br>","zp.dependview.q4":"Why does the Seq.No of a {0} change?<br>","zp.dependview.q5":"Why are some closed {0} listed and some of them aren't?<br>","zp.dependview.q6":"Set Valid Dependency. {0} dates may have conflict. What does it mean ?<br>","zp.dependview.q7":"{0} cannot be closed. Kindly close all the parent {0}(s) before closing this {0}. What does it mean ?","zp.dependview.start":"Start","zp.dependview.taskdetails":"{0} Details","zp.dependview.tasklist":"Task List Name","zp.dependview.taskname":"{0} Name","zp.dependview.taskowner":"{0} Owner","zp.depstatus.blocking":"Blocks {0} {1}(s).","zp.depstatus.blocking":"Blocks {0} {1}(s).","zp.depstatus.waiting":"Waiting for {0} {1}(s).","zp.depstatus.waiting":"Waiting for {0} {1}(s).","zp.desciption.maxlimit":"Description entered here is too large. Some of the information will not be saved. Do you want to proceed?","zp.description.cantbemorethan100":"Description cannot exceed 100 characters","zp.deskinteg.error":"We can't connect to Zoho Desk right now.","zp.desks.task":"Desk {0}","zp.desktop.notify.content":"Stay up to date on your project activities.","zp.desktop.notify.dismiss":"Dismiss","zp.desktop.notify.title":"Desktop Notification","zp.desktop.notify.turnon":"Turn On","zp.details.moreinfo":"More Information","zp.detailsforum.disas":"Disassociate from this {0}","zp.diclaimer.check":"Disclaimer cannot have more than 800 characters","zp.directoryAdmin.settings.description":"Only admin users can configure this integration. Please contact your Zoho Directory admin.","zp.directoryInstall.settings.create":"Create Zoho Directory Accounts","zp.directoryInstall.settings.description":"You cannot configure this integration since you don\u2019t have a Zoho directory account.","zp.directoryService.ads.description":"Synchronize all user identity data from Active directory to the Zoho Directory Admin Panel with ease.","zp.directoryService.ads.title":"Active Directory Sync","zp.directoryService.ads.urlName":"Manage","zp.directoryService.sia.description":"Enhance organizational security with details of user location, number of active devices and their IP addresses.","zp.directoryService.sia.title":"Sign-in Activity","zp.directoryService.sia.urlName":"View","zp.directoryService.sp.description":"Verify employee identity with strict password policies, multi-factor authentication, and ma