rmuladescription.datetimediff":"Returns the difference between the two specified dates in the given units.Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.day":"Returns the day value of the given date parameter as a number from 1 through 31.Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.fromnow":"Calculates the duration between the current date and the given date.Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.hour":"Returns the local time hour value of the given date parameter as a number from 0 (12:00am) through 23 (11:00pm).Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.if":"Evaluates the logic and returns value1 if true or else returns value2.","zp.formuladescription.int":"Returns the integer that is less than or equal to the specified value.","zp.formuladescription.len":"Returns the character count in the given text string.","zp.formuladescription.max":"Returns the largest of the given set of numbers or numeric fields.","zp.formuladescription.min":"Returns the smallest of the given numbers.","zp.formuladescription.minute":"Returns the minute value of the given date parameter as a number from 0 through 59.Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.mod":"Returns the remainder by dividing the value by the divisor.","zp.formuladescription.month":"Returns the month of the given date as a number from 1 through 12.Supported date and time formats: mm-dd-yyyy and hh:mm.","zp.formuladescription.now":"Returns the current date and time.","zp.formuladescription.or":"Evaluates if at least one of given arguments is true.","zp.formuladescription.round":"Returns the integer nearest to the specified value, constraining the new value as per the given precision.","zp.formuladescription.sum":"Calculates the sum of the given numeric values or numeric fields.","zp.formuladescription.today":"Returns today's date and time as 12