"Rename column","zp.header.column.sortingasc":"Sort by Asc (A-Z)","zp.header.column.sortingdesc":"Sort by Desc (Z-A)","zp.header.column.unpin":"Unpin Column","zp.header.column.unpin.msg":"Column unpinned","zp.header.data":"Data preferences","zp.header.reportandchart":"Reports","zp.heldoc.addfirstcollabrate.process":"Collaborate your needs","zp.heldoc.addfirstcollabrate.process.help1":"Pages (Wiki) - a content management system for your project where users can add, modify, or delete content in collaboration with others. Content is added via WYSIWYG editor.","zp.heldoc.addfirstcollabrate.process.help2":"Chat - a text messaging system that allows users to communicate / collaborate with other active users instantly.","zp.heldoc.addfirstdocument":"Upload documents","zp.heldoc.addfirstdocument.help1":"The documents module allows project users to upload and manage documents that are required for the project.","zp.heldoc.addfirstdocument.help2":"Word document, Spreadsheet and Powerpoint Presentation can be edited online.","zp.heldoc.addfirstmessage":"Create a forum message","zp.heldoc.addfirstmessage.help":"Forum is an area where users share thoughts, ideas, or help others by posting messages.","zp.heldoc.addfirststatus":"Post your status","zp.heldoc.addfirststatus.help1":"You can broadcast your current status - such as being busy or what you are currently working on - to the other project users.","zp.heldoc.addfirststatus.help2":"Direct message can be sent to a specific user or set of users. e.x: @[user name] [content]","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask":"Project planning","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask.help1":"You can plan the project activities with the help of milestones and {0}.","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask.help2":"Milestone is a phase of the project. {0} is the actual work item that should be accomplished within a specified period of time.","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask.tlist":"Add New Task & Task List","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask.tlist.help1":"Task - the actual work item that needs to be accomplished within a defined period of time.","zp.heldoc.addfirsttask.tlist.help2":"Task List - an option that allows you to group / organise the relevant {0} together.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.color":"Color!","zp.heldoc.bugsview.color.help1":"Love the idea of differentiating statuses using the color of the board? Use the inverted arrow and pick the color you like to have for each of the statuses.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.expandcollapse":"Adjustable Viewing Area","zp.heldoc.bugsview.expandcollapse.help1":"The &quot;expand / collapse view&quot; option allows you to see more information about the bug in the list view.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.field":"Different field views","zp.heldoc.bugsview.field.help1":"By default, the Kanban view displays the bugs based on their status. In addition, bugs can be viewed based on Severity, Classification, Module and Is It Reproducible.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.listkanban":"View Types","zp.heldoc.bugsview.listkanban.help1":"There are two types of views available in the bugs module: the List view and the newly launched Kanban view.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.listkanban.help2":"Kanban cards are an easy, dynamic way to create and visualize your workflow. In the Kanban View, bugs are arranged in columns based on their status such as To be tested, In progress and Complete. This makes sure everyone in the team knows what\u2019s required to be done at any time.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.viewtype":"Default and Compact View","zp.heldoc.bugsview.viewtype.help1":"Default view - the complete bug title will be visible to the user.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.viewtype.help2":"Compact view - only the first 50 characters of the bug title are visible. To see the complete bug title, just place the mouse over the title.","zp.heldoc.bugsview.viewtype.help3":"The benefit of compact view is more bugs can be seen at a time.","zp.heldoc.importandexport":"Import & Export {0}","zp.heldoc.importandexport.help1":"Import {0} - {0} maintained in an excel or csv or json file can be imported into Zoho Projects.","zp.heldoc.importandexport.help2":"Export {0} - {0} of any specific user or all project users can be exported in excel or csv format.","zp.heldoc.milestone.taskreport":"Gannt & Task Reports","zp.heldoc.milestone.taskreport.help1":"Milestones - each phase of the project can be milestone in Zoho Projects. Start and End Dates are mandatory. Only one user can be assigned as the owner.","zp.heldoc.milestone.taskreport.help2":"Task Reports - displays the report of open tasks by owner, milestone and priority; closed tasks by owner.","zp.heldoc.subtask.reminder.recurring":"Info about Sub-tasks, {0} Reminders and Recurring {1}","zp.heldoc.subtask.reminder.recurring.help1":"Sub-tasks - provides the flexibility to split a {0} and manage them effectively.","zp.heldoc.subtask.reminder.recurring.help2":"{0} Reminders - notifies the {0} owner(s) up-to 30 days prior to the due date.","zp.heldoc.subtask.reminder.recurring.help3":"Recurring {1} - avoids the need of creating the same {0} every week or month. Create the {0} once and set the required recurring frequency.","zp.heldoc.taskotherview":"Other views (Gantt, Dependency)","zp.heldoc.taskotherview.help1":"Dependency view - a view where the dependency between {0} can be established. The supported dependency model is Finish to Start.","zp.heldoc.taskotherview.help2":"Gantt view - a graphical representation of Open/Closed {0}/Milestones.","zp.heldoc.taskview":"Types of views (Classic, Plain, Kanban, Dependency)","zp.heldoc.taskview.help1":"These four are the types of views in {0} & Milestones section.","zp.heldoc.taskview.help2":"Classic view - task-list and its associated {0} are listed.","zp.heldoc.taskview.help3":"Plain view - {0} are listed based on the due date. All {0} and its dependencies are displayed with a tree icon.","zp.heldoc.taskview.help4":"Kanban view - an easy, dynamic way to create and visualise your workflows. Task-list is represented as a board, {0} are places as cards. {0} can be moved between task-lists easily through drag & drop.","zp.holidaylist.addsuccess":"Holiday List added","zp.holidaylist.deletesuccess":"Holiday List deleted","zp.holidaylist.entervalidholidayname":"Enter a valid holiday name","zp.holidaylist.entervalidname":"Enter a valid holiday list name","zp.holidaylist.holidaynameexceedschar":"Holiday name cannot exceed 100 characters","zp.holidaylist.limitreached":"You have reached the maximum number of holiday lists that can be created. Please contact support for more details.","zp.holidaylist.nameexceedschar":"Holiday list name cannot exceed 100 characters","zp.holidaylist.pop.confirmholidaylistdelete":"This action will permanently remove the holiday list data. Are you sure you want to delete this holiday list?","zp.holidaylist.pop.deleteholidaylist":"Delete Holiday List?","zp.holidaylist.pop.holidayinfo":"Holiday Info","zp.holidaylist.pop.updateholidaylist":"Update Holiday List?","zp.holidaylist.updatesuccess":"Holiday List updated","zp.holidays.copyfromlastyear":"Copy From Last Year","zp.holidays.import":"Holidays Import","zp.holidays.import.selecthlist":"Select at least one holiday list","zp.holidays.importlimit":"{0} holidays lists with {1} holidays have been {2} via import.","zp.holidays.importlistoffields":"List of fields in holidays {0} file","zp.holidays.importselection":"The first 500 holidays will be selected and the default values will be mapped to the mismatched fields and fields that are marked &quot;none&quot;. Do you want to continue?","zp.holidays.importsuccess":"{0} holidays lists with {1} holidays have been added and {2} holiday lists with {3} holidays have been updated via import.","zp.holidays.maxlimit":"A maximum of 500 holidays can be imported.","zp.home.lateby":"Late By","zp.home.me":"me","zp.home.more":"More","zp.home.myeve":"You don't have any scheduled events.","zp.home.myexpense":"My Expense","zp.home.myprojects":"Projects","zp.home.project":"Project","zp.home.recentprojects":"Recent Projects","zp.home.space":"Space","zp.hom