umbering.emptygroupprefix":"Please enter Project Group Prefix","zp.numbering.emptyprefix":"Please enter project prefix","zp.numbering.emptytiprefix":"Prefix cannot be empty.","zp.numbering.groupprefixlengthexceeded":"Project Group Prefix must not exceed 10 characters.","zp.numbering.groupprefixvalidation":"Project Group Prefix can only contain alphabets and numbers.","zp.numbering.info":"{2} and {0} will be appended with -T and -I.","zp.numbering.lengthexceeded":"Project prefix cannot exceed 10 characters.","zp.numbering.planalert":"Upgrade your plan to modify this setting.","zp.numbering.prefix":"{1} & {0} Prefix","zp.numbering.prefixconfiguration":"Prefix & ID","zp.numbering.prefixname":"Project Prefix","zp.numbering.prefixvalidation":"The project prefix can only contain alphabets and numbers.","zp.numbering.prefixwaring":"Project prefix cannot be updated if the Project Group Prefix is enabled or Project Prefix is disabled.","zp.numbering.projectgroupprefix":"Project Group Prefix","zp.numbering.projectgroupprefixconfiguration":"Project Group Prefix helps you identify and track projects using a prefix appended.","zp.numbering.projectgroupprefixcontent":"Project Group Prefix allows you to set a custom prefix for every project group.","zp.numbering.projectgroupprefixinfo":"Default project prefix value will be used if project group prefix is not updated.","zp.numbering.projectprefixcontent":"The Project ID is a prefix appended to a unique number that allows you to identify and track projects. The Project prefix must be no more than ten characters long and can only contain letters and numbers.","zp.numbering.taskandissueprefix":"{1} & {0} Prefix","zp.numbering.taskprefixname":"{1} Prefix","zp.numbering.tilengthexceeded":"Prefix cannot exceed 10 characters.","zp.numbering.uniqueprefix":"Please enter a unique prefix.","zp.numberingannounce.content1":"You can now modify the Prefix & ID Setting!","zp.numberingannounce.content2":"Watch Later","zp.numberingannounce.content3":"Video not Supported","zp.numberingannounce.content4":"Projects, Tasks & Issues will have an auto-generated unique ID with a prefix.","zp.numberingannounce.content5":"Navigate to Org Settings in Portal Configuration to <b>enable/disable</b> unique IDs.","zp.numberingannounce.content6":"Update Task & Issue Prefix while you edit a project.","zp.numberingannounce.content7":"With the unique IDs, you can:","zp.numberingannounce.content8":"Search tasks and issues within your project with their unique IDs.","zp.numberingannounce.content9":"#mention the task/issue ID to include it in the status and also in comments anywhere across projects.","zp.o365.settings.disabled":"disabled Microsoft 365 and Outlook integration.","zp.o365.settings.enabled":"enabled Microsoft 365 and Outlook integration.","zp.office.addevent":"Add to Microsoft Outlook Calendar","zp.office.addtask":"Add {0} to Microsoft Outlook {1}","zp.office.authenticate":"to authenticate your account.","zp.office.authfailure":"Your authentication failed.","zp.office.card":"Manage Action Cards","zp.office.carddesc":"Outlook Action cards are sent along with the {0} or issue email notifications from Zoho Projects. Portal users can perform instant actions like assigning work items, setting due dates and modifying their priority, right from their Outlook mailbox using action cards. If you disable this option, email notifications sent from Zoho Projects will not have actionable cards.","zp.office.config":"You are almost there! Just one more step and you are done with integrating Microsoft 365!","zp.office.contactadmin":"Contact your Portal Admin.","zp.office.definition":"Zoho Projects integrates seamlessly with your Microsoft 365 account. Add {0} as events in your Microsoft Outlook calendar and import users from Microsoft 365 account to Zoho Projects.","zp.office.disable":"Disable","zp.office.disabled":"Microsoft 365 and Outlook configuration has been uninstalled successfully","zp.office.enable":"to integrate Microsoft 365 and Outlook.","zp.office.enablecard":"Enable action cards","zp.office.enabled":"Microsoft 365 and Outlook configuration has been installed successfully","zp.office.import":"Import Users from Microsoft 365","zp.office.importfrmofc":"Import from Microsoft 365","zp.office.importnow":"Import Now","zp.office.knowmore":"Know More.","zp.office.name":"Microsoft 365 and Outlook","zp.office.notenabled":"Import your Microsoft 365 users to Zoho Projects","zp.office.nousers":"You don't have any users to import right now.","zp.office.search":"Key in the first 3 letters of a name and click 'Search' to import users from Microsoft 365.","zp.office.selectrole":"Select Role","zp.office.user":"user imported successfully.","zp.office.users":"users imported successfully.","zp.office.userselected":"user selected.","zp.office.usersselected":"users selected.","zp.officeuser.tag":"Microsoft 365 user","zp.onboard.bugkanban":"Bugs Kanban","zp.onboard.calendarcont":"See all of your milestones, tasks, issues and events on the same page.","zp.onboard.projadmin":"Project Administration","zp.onboard.taskkanban":"Tasks Kanban","zp.onboard.taskkanbancont":"The Kanban board is a representation of tasks as cards placed in different columns.","zp.onboarding.acccreated":"Account Created","zp.onboarding.addbug":"Add Issues","zp.onboarding.addmilestone":"Add Milestones","zp.onboarding.addproject":"Add Project","zp.onboarding.addtasktasklist":"Add Task Lists & Tasks","zp.onboarding.adduser":"Add Users","zp.onboarding.completed1":"Kudos!","zp.onboarding.completed10":"Track duration for tasks and issues using","zp.onboarding.completed11":"Global timer.","zp.onboarding.completed12":"View and monitor client related","zp.onboarding.completed13":"Invoices and Expenses.","zp.onboarding.completed14":"Track progress using","zp.onboarding.completed15":"Advanced Reports.","zp.onboarding.completed2":"You\u2019re almost done!","zp.onboarding.completed3":"More to explore...","zp.onboarding.completed4":"Set","zp.onboarding.completed5":"Task Custom Fields","zp.onboarding.completed6":"unique to your business requirements.","zp.onboarding.completed7":"Link tasks using","zp.onboarding.completed8":"Dependencies","zp.onboarding.completed9":"from the Gantt chart.","zp.onboarding.datamigration":"Data Migration","zp.onboarding.documentmanagement":"Document Management","zp.onboarding.forumsfordiscuss":"Forums for Discussions","zp.onboarding.importanyapplication":"Import from any applications","zp.onboarding.issuetracking":"Issue Management / Tracking","zp.onboarding.migration":"Do you want to migrate from a different product than the once listed above?","zp.onboarding.moduleselection1":"Focus on what is essential for your business","zp.onboarding.moduleselection2":"Select from the below features to customize the product. These can be modified later.","zp.onboarding.phases":"Phases or Sub-Projects","zp.onboarding.projectmanagement":"Project Management tool from which you want to migrate","zp.onboarding.reportsandcharts":"Reports & Charts","zp.onboarding.setupprogress":"Setup Progress","zp.onboarding.setupzohoprojects":"Setup Zoho {0}","zp.onboarding.startrequest":"Start Request","zp.onboarding.tasklistheader":"Add Task List","zp.onboarding.taskmanagement":"Tasks Management","zp.onboarding.teamsize":"Size of the Team","zp.onboarding.timetracking":"Time Tracking","zp.onboarding.tryit":"Try it","zp.onboardingtour.bugtrackertrial":"Interested in Premium trial?","zp.onboardingtour.gantt":"Gantt chart let's you get a clear prospect of tasks and milestones with the help of Chronology and Milestone Gantt. You can edit, apply filters, and customize your charts.","zp.onboardingtour.gotit":"Got it","zp.onboardingtour.issue":"You can identify, follow and resolve issues using issue tracker.","zp.onboardingtour.issuereports":"Generate Basic and Advanced issue reports using predefined or custom criteria. Also, get an outlook on issue reports based on custom views.","zp.onboardingtour.issuereportsheader":"Issue Reports","zp.onboardingtour.milestone":"Milestones are major to-do lists. For example, a major feature release in a software project can be a milestone.","zp.onboardingtour.next":"Next","zp.onboardingtour.plannedvsactual":"Get assistance from our Planned vs Actual report to know how competently your team works.","zp.onboardingtour.prev":"Prev","zp.onboardingtour.project":"Start creating a new project in your portal.","zp.onboardingtour.projectstrial":"Interested in trial?","zp.onboardingtour.resourceutil":"With Resource Utilization you can track your team\u2019s progress from the beginning to the end of the following week and also delegate tasks effortlessly, all in one page.","zp.onboardingtour.task":"Add tasks and manage them here.","zp.onboardingtour.tasklist":"Task List breakdown milestones into smaller chunks.","zp.onboardingtour.taskreports":"Generate Basic and Advanced task reports using predefined or custom criteria. You can also view reports based on custom views.","zp.onboardingtour.timesheetreports":"Lay eyes on your team\u2019s productivity with respect to time logs generated using Time Log Reports.","zp.onboardingtour.user":"Add users and collaborate with them to advance your projects.","zp.onboardingtour.welcomeissue":"Define, organize, and track any type of issue with Issue tracker. You can keep track of the life cycle of issues and fix them with appropriate resolutions.","zp.onboardingtour.welcomeissueheader":"Issue","zp.onboardingtour.welcomestarttour":"Get Started","zp.onoff":"Off/On","zp.ontimeexport":"has exported {0} details","zp.openai.charlimitexceed":"Input text cannot exceed 12000 characters.","zp.openai.chatgptapikey":"ChatGPT API Key","zp.openai.createactionitems":"Create Action Items","zp.openai.createactionitemsfor":"Create action Items for","zp.openai.definition":"Definition","zp.openai.disablemsg":"Disabling this integration will remove the saved key. Do you want to continue?","zp.openai.elaborate":"Elaborate","zp.openai.enablechatgpt":"Enable ChatGPT","zp.openai.enableintegration":"Generate content using ChatGPT. <a target='_blank' class='pointer link' href='{0}'>Enable</a> this integration to get started.","zp.openai.entertextto":"Enter your input text","zp.openai.formal":"Formal","zp.openai.friendly":"Friendly","zp.openai.generalerror":"We could not generate the content at the moment. Please try after sometime.","zp.openai.generate":"Generate","zp.openai.generatecontent":"Generate content","zp.openai.generatingcontent":"Generating content","zp.openai.getantonyms":"Get antonyms","zp.openai.getsynonyms":"Get synonyms","zp.openai.helptitle":"How will Zia (powered by ChatGPT) help you?","zp.openai.informal":"Informal","zp.openai.insertbelow":"Insert Below","zp.openai.insufficientquota":"The account associated with this key is in the free plan or does not have enough credits.","zp.openai.integdisabledsuccessfully":"Generative AI disabled","zp.openai.integenabledsuccessfully":"Generative AI enabled","zp.openai.invalidkey":"Please enter a valid ChatGPT key","zp.openai.keyupdatedsuccessfully":"ChatGPT key updated","zp.openai.length":"Length","zp.openai.onewordsubstitute":"Substitute with one word","zp.openai.openai":"Generative AI","zp.openai.openaikeyspage":"OpenAI API keys page.","zp.openai.persuasive":"Persuasive","zp.openai.plananactionfor":"Plan an action for","zp.openai.plananeventfor":"Plan an event for","zp.openai.prepareactionplan":"Prepare Action Plan","zp.openai.prepareeventplan":"Prepare Event Plan","zp.openai.privacy":"Data Privacy Notice","zp.openai.privacymoreinfo":"For more information, please refer to OpenAI's","zp.openai.privacynotice":"This integration allows users to: Fine tune content based on suggestions. Check for language errors and improve tone of the text. Receive contextual suggestions based on input.","zp.openai.privacynotice1":"Please exercise discretion when using this service if your query to OpenAI contains confidential or personal information.","zp.openai.privacyproceed":"By clicking &quot;Proceed&quot;, you acknowledge and accept the risks and the terms of this integration.","zp.openai.punctuate":"Punctuate","zp.openai.regenerate":"Regenerate","zp.openai.rephrase":"Rephrase","zp.openai.replace":"Replace","zp.openai.settings.disabled":"disabled ChatGPT integration","zp.openai.settings.enabled":"enabled ChatGPT integration","zp.openai.setupnote":"Zia powered by ChatGPT, allows users to generate Al based content and fine tune their text. ChatGPT is an artificial intelligence chatbot developed by OpenAl. It is built on top of OpenAl's GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 families of large language models and has been fine-tuned using both supervised and reinforcement learning techniques.","zp.openai.setupnote1":"ChatGPT integration in Zoho Projects allows users to generate Al based content and fine tune their text.","zp.openai.setupnote2":"Access intelligent content suggestions for project, {0}, issue, & forum descriptions based on title. ","zp.openai.setupnote3":"Fine tune content and rephrase text based on multiple options provided within the text editor.","zp.openai.shortern":"Shorten","zp.openai.termsofuse":"OpenAI is an external service based out the USA. Zoho Projects utilizes Open AI's ChatGPT API, subject to OpenAI's Terms of Use","zp.openai.tone":"Tone","zp.openai.typetoaskzia":"Type @ to mention users, # to mention a {1} or {0}, or // to generate content using Zia.","zp.openai.usesuggestion":"Use Suggestion","zp.openai.visitthe":"<a target='_blank' class='link fs13px' href='{0}'>Click here</a> to get the API key.","zp.openai.writeadescription":"Write a Description","zp.openai.writeadescriptionfor":"Write a description for","zp.openai.writeasummary":"Write a Summary","zp.openai.writeasummaryfor":"Write a summary for","zp.openai.writecontent":"Enter to write content","zp.openai.ziasuggestion":"Suggested Content","zp.option.replaceanddelete":"Replace & Delete","zp.organizetab.adminnote":"Default and Custom Modules can be organized according to your preference to make them more accessible. Drag and drop the modules to change their order.","zp.organizetab.cannotremove.module":"This module can't be removed from this project since it is mapped with all the projects.","zp.organizetab.cannotremove.webtab":"This Webtab can't be removed from this project since it is mapped with all the projects.","zp.organizetab.clientnote":"Default and Custom Modules can be organized according to your preference to make them more accessible.","zp.organizetab.confirm.remove.module":"Are you sure you want to remove this module?","zp.organizetab.confirm.remove.webtab":"Are you sure you want to remove this webtab?","zp.organizetab.remove.action":"Remove","zp.organizetab.remove.module":"Remove Module","zp.organizetab.remove.webtab":"Remove Webtab","zp.otherlog.mandatory":"Other Log Entries is a mandatory field","zp.overdue":"Overdue","zp.ownerbulk.adddesc":"Selected users will be added as {0} owners without affecting existing assignment.","zp.ownerbulk.addtitle":"Add Owners","zp.ownerbulk.replacedesc":"Selected users will replace the existing {0} owners.","zp.ownerbulk.replacetitle":"Replace {0} Owners","zp.ownerbulk.swapdesc":"Replace an existing {0} owner with another user. Other {0} owners will not be affected.","zp.ownerbulk.swaptitle":"Switch {0} Owner","zp.ownerbulk.unassigndesc":"Removes current {0} owners. The {0} will be unassigned.","zp.ownerbulk.unassignselecteddesc":"Selected users will be unassigned from the {0}.","zp.ownerbulk.unassignselectedtitle":"Unassign Selected Owners","zp.ownerbulk.unassigntitle":"Unassign {0}","zp.ownerwise.status":"Project Status by Owner","zp.ownerwise.status":"Project Status by Owner","zp.pagetour.content1":"View the most frequently visited project details as widgets.","zp.pagetour.content10":"Sort projects and templates based on their fields.","zp.pagetour.content11":"Customize the project widgets that you frequently track and view their details.","zp.pagetour.content12":"Drag and drop the project widgets and reorder for your convenience.","zp.pagetour.content13":"View the completed percentage of the work items in the selected chart type.","zp.pagetour.content14":"Select the option to create a new task or tasklist.","zp.pagetour.content15":"Reorder tasklists and view the completed tasklists too. Also, import and export tasks.","zp.pagetour.content16":"Customize the columns in Classic view based on the task details that you frequently view.","zp.pagetour.content17":"Any action related to tasklist is done here. You can edit or delete a tasklist, or move a tasklist across projects.","zp.pagetour.content18":"Sort tasks based on their priority, start or end date, etc. You can also permanently save the sorted tasks.","zp.pagetour.content19":"Select a task or multiple tasks to update details at one go. You can update task details such as their priority, owner and more.","zp.pagetour.content2":"Click and navigate to the respective widget for more project details.","zp.pagetour.content20":" Sort Kanban cards the way you want to view. View the cards based on Tasklist, Priority of tasks, Completed percentage of tasks or Status.","zp.pagetour.content21":"Create a new task directly in the Kanban view.","zp.pagetour.content22":"You can drag and drop kanban cards across the tasklist, priority, percentage and status.","zp.pagetour.content23":" Edit, and delete tasklists directly in the kanban view based on your need.","zp.pagetour.content24":"Create a new task directly in the kanban view.","zp.pagetour.content25":"Click this icon to set a color that matches your status.","zp.pagetour.content26":"Search {0} based on their predefined and custom views.","zp.pagetour.content27":"Filter the {0} based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content28":"Other actions on {0} like import, export, settings, and changesets can be done from here.","zp.pagetour.content29":"Customize the columns in List view based on the {0} details that you frequently view.","zp.pagetour.content3":"Quickly add work items like Status, Tasks, Milestones, etc to the project schedule.","zp.pagetour.content30":"Select a {1} or multiple {0} to update details at one go. You can update {1} details such as their due date, severity, status and more.","zp.pagetour.content31":"You can view the cards based on the status, severity, module,classification, and if it's reproducible.","zp.pagetour.content32":"You can drag and drop the kanban cards across the board.","zp.pagetour.content33":"Set the color to differentiate the various bug status.","zp.pagetour.content34":"You can also, directly submit bugs in the Kanban view.","zp.pagetour.content35":"Create a new milestone for your project.","zp.pagetour.content36":"Filter the milestones based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content37":"Edit, complete, or delete milestones. Also, view the release note on the closed tasks and {0}.","zp.pagetour.content38":"Sort milestones based on your perspective to view the milestone details.","zp.pagetour.content39":"Reorder milestones based on convenience and save the new order.","zp.pagetour.content4":"View project updates and other team activities exclusively in Feeds, Status, and Activity Stream.","zp.pagetour.content40":" Navigate between months and years to view the project schedule.","zp.pagetour.content41":"View the scheduled and elapsed events of your project schedule.","zp.pagetour.content42":"Filter project events in the calendar based on their criteria.","zp.pagetour.content43":"Access the iCal and Gcal URL for your portal.","zp.pagetour.content44":"View the count of the pending time sheet approvals.","zp.pagetour.content45":"Filter the time logs based on the project users or time span.","zp.pagetour.content46":"Log time for a particular date or for a selected week.","zp.pagetour.content47":"Edit the time log details or delete them if not required.","zp.pagetour.content48":"Select a particular time log or multiple time logs and approve their entry.","zp.pagetour.content49":"Start a discussion with a new forum post.","zp.pagetour.content5":"View the project lists based on different groups.","zp.pagetour.content50":"Filter the forum posts based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content51":"When you make a forum as a sticky post, it will be notified only to the selected project users.","zp.pagetour.content52":"When you announce a forum post, all the project users will be notified.","zp.pagetour.content53":"You can post comments to the forum topics and collaborate with other team members.","zp.pagetour.content54":"You can organize topics in different folders.","zp.pagetour.content55":"Add new project users and assign their roles.","zp.pagetour.content56":"View the different types of users like the selected project users, followers, and viewers.","zp.pagetour.content57":"You can import users from the associated CRM account, as well as export all the project users.","zp.pagetour.content58":"Choose the gantt chart type that you want to view. In Milestone Gantt, Milestones, Tasklists and Tasks are displayed based on their hierarchy in the project. In Chronology Gantt,  only tasks and subtasks are displayed based on the order of their start date in the project.","zp.pagetour.content59":"Resize the panel width of the chart based on your convenience and view more task details such as Completed Percentage, Duration, Start Date, End Date, and Owner.","zp.pagetour.content6":"Filter the projects based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content60":"Filter the gantt chart based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content61":"Search for project users to track their utilization.","zp.pagetour.content62":"Filter the utilization of the resources based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content63":"Learn more about the utilization chart.","zp.pagetour.content64":"View the {0} assigned to the user.","zp.pagetour.content65":"The planned hours for the {0}.","zp.pagetour.content66":"The actual hours taken to complete the {0}.","zp.pagetour.content67":"Planned vs Actual hours indicates work progress of the user based on the difference in their planned and actual hours.","zp.pagetour.content68":"Choose the type of {0} report to track its progress.","zp.pagetour.content69":"Search to view the {0} from the available {1} views.","zp.pagetour.content7":"Create custom fields for projects based on their requirement. Also, classify projects based on their similarities for quick access.","zp.pagetour.content70":"Filter the {0} based on the criteria.","zp.pagetour.content71":"A task layout is made up of sections and fields. You can customize the current layout or create your own layout and associate it with multiple projects.","zp.pagetour.content72":"Click here to add a new layout for customizing your task form. You can build it upon the default layout initially.","zp.pagetour.content73":"Create and associate your own custom field to your layout using drag-and-drop from the data fields available here.","zp.pagetour.content74":"Drag and drop a data field to the default section or the custom section in your layout and set values as necessary.","zp.pagetour.content75":"The fields that aren't associated with the current layout will be available here. Drag and drop to add a field from this list to your layout.","zp.pagetour.content76":"Drag and drop this component to add a new section to your layout. You can add multiple fields in a section.","zp.pagetour.content77":"Get a preview of your task layout here. Remember to save your changes after you preview.","zp.pagetour.content78":"Use color codes to identify different entities on the calendar.","zp.pagetour.content8":"Customize the columns based on the project details that you frequently view.","zp.pagetour.content9":"Edit, and trash projects based on your need.","zp.pagetour.headercontent1":"Project Widgets","zp.pagetour.headercontent10":"Sort","zp.pagetour.headercontent11":"Customize Dashboard","zp.pagetour.headercontent12":"Reorder Project Widgets","zp.pagetour.headercontent13":"Progress Chart","zp.pagetour.he