nd.","zp.pcf.editconfirmlayoutchange":"Custom fields not part of the new layout will be removed from the project and the data will be lost.","zp.pcf.editlayout":"Edit Layout","zp.pcf.layoutpermission":"Layout Permissions","zp.pcf.layoutupgrade":"You can create project layouts only in our user based Enterprise plan. <a target='_blank' class='' href='{0}'>Click here</a> to upgrade your subscription.","zp.pcf.markallformandatory":"Set the field permission to Read & Edit for all profiles to mark this field as mandatory.","zp.pcf.markasnotrequired":"Remove as a mandatory field","zp.pcf.markasrequired":"Mark as mandatory","zp.pcf.markloginnamemandatory":"Edit permissions for this field and enable To Self/To Others for all the profiles to set as mandatory","zp.pcf.newconfirmlayoutchange":"Changing layout will reload the form and delete all changes.<br> Do you wish to Proceed?","zp.pcf.newsectioninfo":"Custom fields cannot be added to default sections. Add this to a custom section.","zp.pcf.profileinfo":"Select the user profiles that can access this layout.","zp.pcf.projectlayoutdesc":"Design your project forms using Layouts. Layouts can be customized using sections and fields.","zp.pcf.sections":"Sections","zp.pcf.statusupdate":"Changes will reflect in all associated layouts.","zp.pcf.tasklayoutdesc":"Design your {0} forms using Layouts. Layouts can be customized using sections and fields.","zp.pcflist.maxalert":"You can enable up to 50 columns","zp.pcflist.maxalertmove":"You can move up to 50 columns","zp.pcflist.minalert":"Minimum 1 column has to be enabled.","zp.pcflist.projectlayout":"Project Layout","zp.pcflist.projectlayouts":"Project Layouts","zp.pcflist.tasklayouts":"{0} Layouts","zp.pcflist.timesheetlayout":"Timesheet Layout","zp.pcflist.timesheetlayouts":"Timesheet Layouts","zp.pcv.enablecustomcolum":"Customize Columns to be Displayed","zp.pcv.exportnote":"Projects in the current view will be exported.","zp.pcv.fieldnotexistwarning":"Some fields are either delete