 our most powerful integrations yet.","zp.people.crma1":"ZSC stands for Zoho Service Communication. it is a key used for interservice communication between two Zoho Services.","zp.people.crma2":"Login into Zoho CRM and click &quot;Setup&quot; link on the top right","zp.people.crma3":"Under &quot;Developer Space&quot; click on &quot;Zoho Service Communication (ZSC) key&quot; link and generate the key","zp.people.crma4":"If you are not in &quot;Admin Role&quot; in Zoho CRM, then you will not have the privilege to generate ZSC key. Contact your Zoho CRM administrator for the same.","zp.people.crmclientemptymsg":"No accounts to import from this CRM account.","zp.people.crmuseranthoracc":"Importing from another account","zp.people.crmuseremptymsg":"No users to import from this CRM account.","zp.people.customizeforuser":"Customize permissions for this user","zp.people.deactivateusersfrompeople":"Deactivate the inactive users of Zoho People in {0}","zp.people.deleteintegration.confirm.message":"Deleting this integration will remove the sync with Zoho People. All leaves will be deleted and will no longer be displayed in the Zoho Projects calendar.","zp.people.deleteintegration.consent.message":"I understand that synced leaves will be deleted and will no longer be available in Zoho Projects","zp.people.deleteuser":"Delete User","zp.people.disablesuccess":"Disabled Successfully","zp.people.employee":"Employee","zp.people.employeeid":"Employee ID","zp.people.enablesuccess":"Enabled Successfully","zp.people.follower":"Follower","zp.people.followmoreproj":"Follow this user in other projects.","zp.people.howtogenerate":"Where can i generate the ZSC Key ?","zp.people.import":"Import users from Zoho People","zp.people.importdet":"Import users from Zoho People and start viewing their data in Zoho {0}. Plan work based on availability of users and stay on track.","zp.people.importfrmpeople":"Import from Zoho People","zp.people.importpeople":"Import Users from Zoho People Account","zp.