l cost of the project in its portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcybudget.desc":"The budget of the current project in portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcycostvariance.desc":"Cost Variance shows deviation from the planned budget in portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcyearnedvalue.desc":"Earned value of a project refers to the actual amount earned in the project based on the actual work done in base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcyforecastedcost.desc":"An estimate of the expenses that will be incurred in the future for a specific current module based on the growing requirement in base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcyplannedcost.desc":"Estimated amount allocated for the current module in base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcyplannedvalue.desc":"Planned Value of a project allows users to know the baseline cost or planned value of the cost of the project at any given point of time in base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.bcyschedulevariance.desc":"Schedule Variance is a measure of the deviation in project schedule in base currency.","zp.script.server.projects.field.billingmethod.desc":"Billing type refers to how the client is charged based on different billing methods available in Zoho projects.","zp.script.server.projects.field.budget.desc":"Fixed budget amount for the entire current module based on different budget types available in Zoho projects.","zp.script.server.projects.field.budgettype.desc":"Budget type based on the types provided in the Zoho projects portal","zp.script.server.projects.field.completedtime.desc":"The time at which a current module was completed.","zp.script.server.projects.field.costvariance.desc":"Cost Variance shows deviation from the planned budget.","zp.script.server.projects.field.createdby.desc":"The user who created the current module.","zp.script.server.projects.field.createdtime.desc":"The time of creation of the current module.","zp.script.server.projects.field.description.desc":"A set of instructions for a specific Project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.earnedvalue.desc":"Earned value of a current module refers to the actual amount earned in the project based on the actual work done.","zp.script.server.projects.field.enddate.desc":"Ending date of the project","zp.script.server.projects.field.forecastedcost.desc":"An estimate of the expenses that will be incurred in the future for a specific current module based on the growing requirement.","zp.script.server.projects.field.forecastedhours.desc":"An estimate of the hours taken to complete a Project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.forecastedrevenue.desc":"An estimate of the revenue that will be generated by a Project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.hourlybudget.desc":"Budget based on hours per Project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.hourlybudgetthreshold.desc":"The maximum amount that can be spent on a current module based on hours.","zp.script.server.projects.field.invoicedamount.desc":"The amount invoiced so far at a current given time","zp.script.server.projects.field.issues.desc":"The bugs or problems in a project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.layoutid.desc":"The id of the current selected layout.","zp.script.server.projects.field.milestone.desc":"The name of the current milestone.","zp.script.server.projects.field.modifiedtime.desc":"Last modified time of the current module","zp.script.server.projects.field.name.desc":"Name of the current module.","zp.script.server.projects.field.nonbillableloghours.desc":"Hours for which the employees are not paid for looging into work.","zp.script.server.projects.field.otherexpenses.desc":"Extra expenses apart from the planned expense criterias.","zp.script.server.projects.field.owner.desc":"Owner of the Project.","zp.script.server.projects.field.percentcomplete.desc":"The completion percentage of current module.","zp.script.server.projects.field.plannedcost.desc":"