ich the user got added to portal.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.allowedloghours.desc":"The time period which the user is allowed to log the working hours.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.balance.desc":"The balance left in the budget allocated for the current task","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyactualcost.desc":"The actual cost of the task in its portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcybudget.desc":"The budget of the current task in portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcycostvariance.desc":"Cost Variance shows deviation from the planned budget in portal's base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyearnedvalue.desc":"Earned value of a project refers to the actual amount earned in the task based on the actual work done in base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyforecastedcost.desc":"An estimate of the expenses that will be incurred in the future for a specific current task based on the growing requirement in base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyplannedcost.desc":"Estimated amount allocated for the current task in base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyplannedvalue.desc":"Planned Value of a task allows users to know the baseline cost or planned value of the cost of the task at any given point of time in base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.bcyschedulevariance.desc":"Schedule Variance is a measure of the deviation in task schedule in base currency.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.billingtype.desc":"Billing type refers to how the client is charged based on different billing methods available in Zoho projects.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.budget.desc":"Fixed budget amount for the entire current task based on different budget types available in Zoho projects.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.budgetthreshold.desc":"The maximum amount that can be spent on a current task.","zp.script.server.tasks.field.completedtime.desc":"The time at which a current task was completed.","zp.script.server.task