"Please enter the minimum and maximum characters allowed for this field.","zp.textfield.maxchar.greaterthan.zero":"Maximum character limit should be greater than 0","zp.textfield.maximumchar":"Please enter a maximum of {1} characters in {0} field","zp.textfield.maxlimit":"Please set a maximum character limit of {0}","zp.textfield.minimumchar":"Please enter a minimum of {1} characters in {0} field","zp.textfield.minlessthanmax":"Minimum character limit cannot be more than the maximum limit","zp.tg.allcat":"All","zp.tg.back":"Back","zp.tg.blankproj":"Blank project","zp.tg.browsetemplate":"Browse Templates","zp.tg.cancel":"Cancel","zp.tg.cat0":"Pharma","zp.tg.cat1":"Marketing/Sales","zp.tg.cat2":"Manufacturing","zp.tg.cat3":"Software/IT","zp.tg.cat4":"Construction","zp.tg.cat6":"HR","zp.tg.cat7":"Others","zp.tg.choosetgallery":"Create a Project from a Template","zp.tg.chsexistin":"(or) Select the existing project from the below listed gallery","zp.tg.createproj":"Create Project","zp.tg.desc1":"With the use of this digital marketing template, you may monitor the development of your marketing strategy as well as SEO, branding, design, and progress toward your objectives. Meet your deadlines while fostering new levels of teamwork.","zp.tg.desc10":"Using this template, you can plan for project risks. Risk will occur, but you can prepare for it by having a response plan in place.","zp.tg.desc11":"Kickoff your next product launch with ready-made task on the board view and defined phases for product delivery and promotion on the Gantt view.","zp.tg.desc12":"Start your sales strategy with our high-level sales template.","zp.tg.desc13":"Are you getting married? Use this wedding checklist to help you plan your wedding without stress. Organize and personalise this template to make your wedding day perfect.","zp.tg.desc14":"Every piece of software must be secure. Customize our software security testing template to meet your specific requirements.","zp.tg.desc15":"SEO necessitates a large number of moving parts and contributors. With our comprehensive SEO template, you can easily manage your SEO activities.","zp.tg.desc16":"Trip planning is the key to a stress-free getaway when it comes to making the most of your time away from the office. Preparing for every aspect of your trip with our high level travel itinerary template is the first step toward total relaxation.","zp.tg.desc17":"It is a good idea to inspect your vehicle on a regular basis. This ensures your and your family's safety. With our template, you can get started quickly.","zp.tg.desc18":"Customize this High level request for proposal (RFP) template to help buyers make informed decisions about business partnerships or purchases by explaining product or service needs to vendors.","zp.tg.desc19":"With this template, you can easily create and repeat processes for conducting UX research.","zp.tg.desc2":"Customize this high-level manufacturing template based on your company's needs.","zp.tg.desc20":"Streamline the onboarding process to ensure that new employees are up to speed and have the knowledge they need to succeed. Everything is done in one location, from pre-onboarding to day one.","zp.tg.desc21":"With this template, you can get a kick start of ZOHO Projects.","zp.tg.desc22":"With this template, you may easily keep track of your accounts and financial statements.","zp.tg.desc23":"With this project template, apartment maintenance becomes a simple.","zp.tg.desc24":"With our Retail store project template, you can easily set up your own retail store.","zp.tg.desc3":"Event planning templates are essential to the success of any event planning team! Starting with a pre-made template simplifies the entire process, from organising venue information and budgets to curating the guest list and tracking attendance!","zp.tg.desc4":"With our pre-defined Template, managing and monitoring your software development project will be a breeze.","zp.tg.desc5":"Your website's pages should be carefully planned, organised, and constructed. Using this template, you can easily keep track of your action plan and make sure that your website is headed in the right direction!","zp.tg.desc6":"One of the most vital resources for any construction team are construction project management templates. It is crucial to streamline your procedure while planning building projects by using a pre-made template.","zp.tg.desc7":"Utilize this template to oversee the creation of your new auto part, from concept to completion.","zp.tg.desc8":"Customize this IT support project template to meet your specific business requirements.","zp.tg.desc9":"Manage the development of new products. This manufacturing template includes pre-production activities, design, production, and release.","zp.tg.donotshow":"Do not show this again","zp.tg.favtemps":"Favorite Templates","zp.tg.fromscratch":"Start everything from scratch","zp.tg.name1":"Digital Marketing","zp.tg.name10":"Risk Tracker","zp.tg.name11":"Product Launch","zp.tg.name12":"Sales Planning","zp.tg.name13":"Wedding Planner","zp.tg.name14":"Security Testing","zp.tg.name15":"SEO","zp.tg.name16":"Travel","zp.tg.name17":"Vehicle inspection","zp.tg.name18":"RFP","zp.tg.name19":"UX Research","zp.tg.name2":"Manufacturing","zp.tg.name20":"Employee Onboarding","zp.tg.name21":"Explore Zoho Projects!","zp.tg.name22":"Accounting","zp.tg.name23":"Apartment Maintenance","zp.tg.name24":"Retail Store","zp.tg.name25":"Quality Control & Assurance in Pharma","zp.tg.name26":"Supply Chain Management for Pharma","zp.tg.name27":"Drug Development & Clinical Trials","zp.tg.name28":"Customer Acquisition Strategy","zp.tg.name29":"Building Maintenance & Renovation","zp.tg.name3":"Event Planner","zp.tg.name30":"Product Launch Plan","zp.tg.name4":"Software Development","zp.tg.name5":"Website Development","zp.tg.name6":"Construction","zp.tg.name7":"Automobile Spare Manufacturing","zp.tg.name8":"IT Support Project","zp.tg.name9":"Manufacturing New Product","zp.tg.new":"New",