rate, or annotate images to convey ideas better.","zp.whiteboard.key4":"Add project users as editors to work collaboratively.","zp.whiteboard.maxnamelength":"Input Parameter Exceeds Maximum Length!","zp.whiteboard.maxuser":"A maximum of 50 users can only be added.","zp.whiteboard.settings.alreadydisabled":"Already disabled Whiteboard integration","zp.whiteboard.settings.alreadyenabled":"Already enabled Whiteboard integration","zp.whiteboard.settings.disabled":"disabled Whiteboard integration.","zp.whiteboard.settings.enabled":"enabled Whiteboard integration.","zp.whiteboard.upgradeportal":"Please upgrade your portal to our latest Enterprise plan to access this feature.","zp.whiteboard.whiteboardrename":"Whiteboard has been renamed successfully","zp.whiteboard.whiteboardupdate":"Whiteboard updated successfully","zp.whitelabel.bugdomainverifyfail":"Domain verification for the email address {0} has failed. This could be due to a missing host name and key value of Zoho BugTracker in the TXT record of your domain manager.","zp.whitelabel.buginfo":"Login to your domain manager and add the generated hostname and key value in the TXT record. You should not remove this from TXT record as long as you use Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugnote2":"Have a great experience with Zoho BugTracker!","zp.whitelabel.bugnotify":"Once approved, your email address {0} will be used to send all email notifications related to your organization <b>{1}</b> in Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugquestion":"This email address will be the 'From' address for notifications sent from Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugreconfig":"You can reconfigure your sender email in Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugstep1":"Go to Setup in Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugsteps":"Steps to enter the verification code in Zoho BugTracker:","zp.whitelabel.bugsuccessmail":"Your email address {0} has been added as the sender email in <b>{1}</b> organization in Zoho BugTracker. You will need to verify the email address {2}. Please enter the verification code shown below in Zoho BugTracker.","zp.whitelabel.bugzohoteam":"Zoho BugTracker Team","zp.whitelabel.change":"Change","zp.whitelabel.copyvalue":"Copy this value","zp.whitelabel.desc1":"We're unable to complete the domain verification process due to one of the following reasons:","zp.whitelabel.desc2":"Delay in configuration changes getting applied/propagated on your DNS manager due to higher TTL (Time To Live) values.","zp.whitelabel.desc3":"Misconfiguration of TXT record on your DNS Manager. You can wait for a day and check the verification status again. We request you to contact {0} if the issue persists.","zp.whitelabel.desc4":"If you have entered an email address with a public domain.","zp.whitelabel.desc5":"If your DNS provider appends the domain name automatically, please provide record name up to domainkey. E.g., 1522905413783._domainkey","zp.whitelabel.domainverifyfail":"Domain verification for the email address {0} has failed. This could be due to a missing host name and key value of Zoho Projects in the TXT record of your domain manager.","zp.whitelabel.emailfailure":"Email address verification failed","zp.whitelabel.emailsuccess":"Email address verified successfully","zp.whitelabel.emptyverifycode":"Enter the verification code sent to your email","zp.whitelabel.failnote":"Going forward, all email notifications will be sent from the default email address notifications@zohoprojects.com.","zp.whitelabel.header":"Your Domain have not been verified yet. Please update your Sender Email","zp.whitelabel.hostname":"Hostname","zp.whitelabel.hostvalue":"Value","zp.whitelabel.info":"Login to your domain manager and add the generated hostname and key value in the TXT record. You should not remove this from TXT record as long as you use Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.link":"Click here to update your domain details in Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.link1":"Please visit the below link to learn more.","zp.whitelabel.mailsent":"Mail Sent","zp.whitelabel.note1":"After your domain is verified, a verification code will be sent to your email. Please enter the code here to verify your email address.","zp.whitelabel.note2":"Have a great experience with Zoho Projects!","zp.whitelabel.notes":"For example, if the email address is john@zylker.com, your email address and the domain zylker.com has to be verified. Click <b>Verify</b> to get a hostname and a value.","zp.whitelabel.notify":"Once approved, your email address {0} will be used to send all email notifications related to your organization <b>{1}</b> in Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.notverified":"Not Verified","zp.whitelabel.publicdomain":"You cannot enter a public domain email address.","zp.whitelabel.question":"This email address will be the 'From' address for notifications sent from Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.reconfig":"You can reconfigure your sender email in Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.resendcode":"Resend verification code","zp.whitelabel.resendmail":"Please check your email for the verification code. Didn't receive the email yet?","zp.whitelabel.sender":"Sender email:","zp.whitelabel.step1":"Go to Setup in Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.step2":"Navigate to the <b>Portal Configuration > Org Settings > Sender Email.</b>","zp.whitelabel.step3":"Enter the verification code and click <b>Verify Email.</b>","zp.whitelabel.steps":"Steps to enter the verification code in Zoho Projects:","zp.whitelabel.successmail":"Your email address {0} has been added as the sender email in <b>{1}</b> organization in Zoho Projects. You will need to verify the email address {2}. Please enter the verification code shown below in Zoho Projects.","zp.whitelabel.title":"Sender Email","zp.whitelabel.update":"The existing configuration will become invalid and the email notifications will be sent from the default address (notifications@zohoprojects.com).","zp.whitelabel.validaddress":"Enter a valid email address. Eg: steveb@zylker.com","zp.whitelabel.verified":"