be able to access the documents once the migration is complete.","zp.workdrive.migration.docstab.header":"Migration In Progress","zp.workdrive.migration.fheading":"A dedicated Folder will be created for each project in WorkDrive. Documents and attachments from each project will be moved to its respective Folder. You can access your documents after the migration is complete. The following changes will apply:","zp.workdrive.migration.info":"We will start migrating your documents to WorkDrive. This cannot be undone.","zp.workdrive.migration.inprogress":"Migration in Progress","zp.workdrive.migration.later":"Migrate later","zp.workdrive.migration.note":"Note: Project documents will not be accessible during migration.","zp.workdrive.migration.now":"Migrate now","zp.workdrive.migration.p1.c":"You can select or create a WorkDrive team before the migration starts.","zp.workdrive.migration.p10.f":"All the documents and folders within your documents tab will be moved to the Private folder under Zoho Projects > ProjectName-Documents.","zp.workdrive.migration.p11.c":"All the attachments will be moved to the Private folder under Zoho Projects > ProjectName-Attachments.","zp.workdrive.migration.p12.c":"The Documents tab inside projects will not be accessible during migration. Users can add attachments as usual.","zp.workdrive.migration.p13.c":"Migration will start as per the schedule after you click Migrate.","zp.workdrive.migration.p14.c":"You will receive a notification via email once the migration is completed.","zp.workdrive.migration.p2.c":"Portal Owner and Admins will be added as Admins in WorkDrive.","zp.workdrive.migration.p3.c":"Other users will be added as team members.","zp.workdrive.migration.p4.c":"Client users will be added as Guests.","zp.workdrive.migration.p5.t":"Team folders will be created for all the projects in your portal.","zp.workdrive.migration.p6.t":"Project users will be added to the team folder.","zp.workdrive.migration.p7.t":"Project documents will be